{"tid":1228044,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃秋生：點解要對『暴動』低頭？如果唔係『暴動』，係抗議的話，咁點解槍槍打頭呀？","createTime":"2019-06-15T16:14:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T16:29:02.000Z","uid":133611,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"398cc89705d3ad8e6b61d49b2ac6ad7f8e3f9d7b","tid":1228044,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:14:10.000Z","msg":"繼6月9日103萬人上街反送中及連日佔領金鐘示威後，建制派對修例意見昨日突然全部「轉軚」，而全部建制派中人均表示應該暫緩執行，根據今日多個報道指，行政長官林鄭月娥今日下午將見傳媒，宣佈暫緩修例。（相關新聞： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2WHgi78\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2WHgi78&d=YAxVOUHAW5%2FtYfR1oVoe2wKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=bff81cdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2WHgi78</a> ）<br />\n相關新聞：【引渡惡法】不合作運動2.0 網上發起機場「行下坐下接下機」行動<br />\n<br />\n近日非常關注反送中條例事件，更常常於社交網站表達見解的黃秋生，今日接受《蘋果》訪問，問到對政府可能宣佈暫緩修例有何睇法時，秋生回覆說：「（政府）點解要對『暴動』低頭？如果唔係『暴動』，係抗議的話，咁點解槍槍打頭呀？咁啲『父親』（警方）使唔使追究呀？」<br />\n秋生又表示林鄭應該落台換人：「佢搞成咁仲叫佢解說？換人啦！都自己射自己龍門咯，同埋，<span style=\"color: red;\">我懷疑佢識唔識得解說</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190615/59718202?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=share_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190615%2F59718202%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&d=YAxVOUHAW5%2FtYfR1oVoe2wKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=4011fbe5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190615%2F59718202%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&h=b4840898\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190615/59718202?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=share_link</a>"},{"pid":"175fa29c17ad67e8fde01c6be3d7d121ac6ef40c","tid":1228044,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:15:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73aec92205b6c7bf1194c1a022b438de8aa1ef4b","tid":1228044,"uid":27670,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:18:09.000Z","msg":"黃秋生依然故我 敢作敢言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Respect"},{"pid":"02f7d072bb902fcbd3fdccd6f86ff1995258d041","tid":1228044,"uid":160502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:27:38.000Z","msg":"秋生真係香港之光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f56d6e77ebf6213df0d90e25f330ac47f1ead70","tid":1228044,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}